text: Mackenzie Willis (born 7 August 1995) is a former Australian rules footballer playing for the Gold Coast Football Club in the Australian Football League (AFL). He was drafted by the Gold Coast Football Club with their fourth selection and fifty-second overall in the 2015 national draft. He made his debut in the 120 point loss against in round 6, 2016 at Simonds Stadium.
